<Content>absolutey NOT up to 3-star admittedly, this hotel is well and centrally located, which, however, enables it to provide less due service. two examples, it claims that wlan connection is available in rooms, but i have changed 3 times (testing one after another) to find a room that was within signal coverage, but still very unstable connections. so if you plan to carry ur laptop here, please find another hotel or find a internet cafe nearby, second disappointment, this hotel shockingly doesnt offer laundry service. when i carried a bag of shirts down to the reception asking where should i leave them, the receptionist said, there is a laundry around the corner, please do it youeself and we dont have laundry. i couldnt believe it, 3 stars without laundry?!! breakfast is ok, dont expect too much though.generally good location, but if you dont really need that that central location, please find another hotel to spare the troubles. 
