<Content>Great Location I found this hotel through tripadvisor and was very pleased with my stay. Not enough can be said about the helpful staff at the front desk. At the end of my stay, they even called ahead to my next hotel to be sure that my reservation was confirmed.The location cannot be beat. You are within walking distance to all the sights and museums.The hotel does need to replace worn towels, sheets, bedspreads, and carpeting. It would make a difference in its appearance.While in Berlin I took 4 of the Original Insider Tours. They were superb and gave you great value for your dollar. You can find brochures for the tours in this hotel's lobby. 
