<Author>SilverPearl
<Content>A pleasant stay at the Hotel Kubrat This hotel equipped with an elevator is located conveniently near the Potsdamer Platz train station. Though it is located along a busy street, our large, clean room in contrast was very quiet. English-speaking staff members were pleasant and helpful. The continental breakfast was great, and an adjacent Italian restaurant served good food. The hotel provided free use of the Internet on a computer outside the lobby. The Checkpoint Charlie Museum, Brandenburg Gate, Reichstag and Holocaust Memorial are within walking distance. 
